H3.text: Brunswick, Lancastrian and Pearl Pickler are types of which vegetable. Pyaz

A4.text: Those cucumbers intended for pickling, called picklers, grow to about 7 to 10 cm (3 to 4 in) long and 2.5 cm (1 in) wide.

A5.text: Commercial pickles are made from cucumbers specially bred for uniformity of length-to-diameter ratio and lack of voids in the flesh.
